lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur manager Mauricio Pochettino has urged forward Vincent Janssen to make the most of injured Harry Kane's absence in Saturday's Premier League clash against Middlesbrough.

headline.print_headline: Pochettino Backs Janssen to Fill Kane Void for Spurs
headline.main: Pochettino Backs Janssen to Fill Kane Void for Spurs
